Hey I have just started a club for non toxic players(doesn&#039;t mean you cant get a bit salty just not every game flamers or feeders), and I have a hand full of people already but would like to invite anyone (pref lower tier players to match us gold V and below) to join us so we can start a less toxic community and play customs, 5 man ranked/norms so we don&#039;t have to be put with toxic players and can have the enjoyment of playing with mates, if we got enough players might host tournies with _**RP prizes**_ n such, the main goal is to make this game less of a grind and more of an enjoyable thing to do, so feel free to send me and friend invite, or leave a comment and ill add you

